This program plays a very
old  Japanese game called
GOMOKU  (also  known as 5
in line and Pente).   The
board has  19x19 squares;
Get 5 stones in a row and
you win!




HOW TO MOVE

Use  the  keypad  keys to
move the cursor:

    Home    PgUp

      Ä     Ä

     End    PgDn

Touch <RETURN> or <SPACE>
to make your move.

USING THE MENU

Use  the  menu  above  to
perform  these   commands
(type the first letter):

  N - Start a new game
  Q - Exit the program
  A - Program plays alone
  P - Switch sides
  H - Get a hint

